# data source: thoth_api_key_authorization

```terraform
data "thoth_api_key_authorization" "execute_check" {
  key_id        = var.key_id
  api_key       = var.api_key
  permission    = "execute"
  resource_type = "agent"
  resource_id   = var.agent_id
}
```
